[http://d-link.com/products/default.aspx?pid=VWR-VR&tab=3 Support page] OEM Alpha Networks This router is designed for use with the Vonage VoIP service. There is a Legerity Le88241DLC on-board. There is no FCC ID printed on the exterior of the device. The Mini PCI wireless module has a label with the FCC ID.. but it is covered (and prevented from removal) by a metal shield soldered on after insertion of the card. ==Images== File:D-Link VWR-VR rev B1 board top.jpg|board top [[Has images::internal| ]]
